1.Install Node

2. Run Command
	. npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer vite
	. npx tailwindcss init -p

3. tailwind.config.js file mei jaake-------> content: ["*"]

4. package.json mei gye    ----->  "scripts": {
   			        	"start":"vite"
  			            }

5. main.css file bnani hai usme yeh 3 paste krni hai-:
	  @tailwind base;
	  @tailwind components;
	  @tailwind utilities;

6. Link krni hai main.css html mei

7. To run the code run command
	      npm run start
